OL,3,CProposed hosepipe ban first weekend of
OL,4,Cthe summer holidays
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water has issued a
OL,7,Fwarning that a hosepipe ban may come
OL,8,Finto action this weekend (18-19 July).
OL,10,FThe ban could cover mid and south
OL,11,FCeredigion, parts of north
OL,12,FPembrokeshire, alongside north
OL,13,FCarmarthenshire and would be a short-
OL,14,Fterm emergency measure to help protect
OL,15,Fsupplies.
OL,17,FThe company says that the prolonged
OL,18,Fhot weather and increased demand for
OL,19,Fdrinking water has led to the
OL,20,Fproposition.
OL,26,@nD@Bs{
