CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784224106
OL,3,CProposed hosepipe ban first weekend of
OL,4,Cthe summer holidays
OL,6,FIt says that around one billion litres
OL,7,Fof water have been put into supply
OL,8,Feach day over the last week, which is
OL,9,Fup about 20% more than usual at this
OL,10,Ftime of year.
OL,12,FDwr Cymru has made it clear that
OL,13,Funless "demand reduces significantly
OL,14,Fover the next few days", it will have
OL,15,Fno choice but to introduce a temporary
OL,16,Frestriction on hosepipes.
