CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784224106
OL,3,CProposed hosepipe ban first weekend of
OL,4,Cthe summer holidays
OL,6,FCurrently the organisation is taking
OL,7,F'extensive' measures to maintain
OL,8,Fsupplies, including water treatment,
OL,9,Fadditional movement across the
OL,10,Fnetwork, the reservoirs are 'being
OL,11,Fkept as full as possible', increased
OL,12,Fattention to leaks, and all round
OL,13,Fhigher levels of support.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
