FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784224106
OL,3,CProposed hosepipe ban first weekend of
OL,4,Cthe summer holidays
OL,6,FChief Customer Officer, Kit Wilson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are now reaching the point
OL,8,Fwhere, unless demand reduces
OL,9,Fsignificantly over the next few days,
OL,10,Fwe are likely to have no option but to
OL,11,Fintroduce temporary hosepipe
OL,12,Frestrictions this weekend to help
OL,13,Fprotect essential water supplies and
OL,14,Freduce the risk of customers
OL,15,Fexperiencing low pressure or
OL,16,Finterruptions to supply".
OL,18,FMr Wilson added that it is not a
OL,19,Fdecision they want to take but they
OL,20,Fintend to consider and act in the
OL,21,Fcustomers best interest.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
