FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784224106
OL,3,CProposed hosepipe ban first weekend of
OL,4,Cthe summer holidays
OL,6,FHe continued: "There is still an
OL,7,Fopportunity to avoid these
OL,8,Frestrictions if everyone plays their
OL,9,Fpart by reducing non-essential water
OL,10,Fuse now. Every litre saved will help
OL,11,Fus keep taps flowing for homes,
OL,12,Fbusinesses and essential services
OL,13,Facross the affected area".
OL,15,FCustomers are urged to avoid
OL,16,Funnecessary and excessive water use
OL,17,Fwhilst they monitor conditions before
OL,18,Freaching a decision.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
